show.title: Gone, Yet Loved By Him

show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/KKwe24
show.description: Bellway Zouch and Eason Gold shared three years together, but their love was unequal. When Bellway discovered that Eason had always harbored feelings for his childhood sweetheart, Celine Moody, and had merely seen her as a substitute, she decided to leave the country to study abroad. At her mother's request, she gave herself a month to slowly detach from Eason. In this month, she gradually came to terms with her past and found the strength to move on. On the day she left, Eason finally realized that the one he truly loved was always Bellway…
